<db:abstract>
<db:para>A request for showing a HTML5 form validation message to the user.</db:para>
<db:para><db:emphasis role="bold">This type is deprecated. We strongly advise against using it in new code.</db:emphasis></db:para>
<db:para>This type was introduced in QtWebEngine 1.4.</db:para>
</db:abstract>
